[{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"taxonomy","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"Authors","url":"/authors/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"section","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"Blogs","url":"/blog/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"taxonomy","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"Categories","url":"/categories/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"home","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"clsty 时空（主页）","url":"/","year":"0001"},{"categories":["TestCategory"],"date":-62135596800,"headings":[{"anchor":"配置为默认选择上次选择的内核来启动","title":"配置为默认选择上次选择的内核来启动"}],"kind":"page","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"（测试文章）\n配置为默认选择上次选择的内核来启动 编辑 /etc/default/grub 并添加：\n1GRUB_SAVEDEFAULT=true 2GRUB_DEFAULT=saved ","tags":["TestTag"],"title":"GRUB2","url":"/blog/1/01/grub2/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"page","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"Redirect your life.","title":"My Song","url":"/posts/redirector/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"section","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"Posts","url":"/posts/","year":"0001"},{"categories":["TestCategory"],"date":-62135596800,"headings":[{"anchor":"rsync-的-a","title":"rsync 的 -a"}],"kind":"page","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"rsync 的 -a -a 即 –archive，它相当于 -rlptgoD ，分别解释如下：\n-r（–recursive）：以递归方式复制文件。这将使rsync复制目录及其所有内容，包括子目录和文件。 -l（–links）：保留符号链接。当源目录中存在符号链接时，该选项将复制符号链接的目标文件而不是符号链接本身。 -p（–perms）：保留文件的权限。使用该选项将保留文件的所有权和读/写/执行权限。 -t（–times）：保留文件的时间戳。使用该选项将复制源文件的修改时间和访问时间到目标文件。 -g（–group）：保留文件所属组。通过指定该选项，rsync将保留文件所属组而不进行更改。 -o（–owner）：保留文件所有者。该选项保留每个文件的所有者身份而不进行更改。 -D：保留特殊设备和特殊文件。 ","title":"Rsync","url":"/blog/1/01/rsync/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"taxonomy","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"Series","url":"/series/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596800,"headings":[],"kind":"taxonomy","lang":"zh-hans","summary":"","title":"Tags","url":"/tags/","year":"0001"},{"date":-62135596